{"tid":1140782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李倩怡　林榮基　出席同一網上直播　5月7日星期二8:30pm","createTime":"2019-05-06T05:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T13:17:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fc99dacea4f8bf802d815b93befec82a82a964","tid":1140782,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chenyichi.radicalwing/photos/a.309038275950197/1091185011068849/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchenyichi.radicalwing%2Fphotos%2Fa.309038275950197%2F1091185011068849%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkNw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=f0f45b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chenyichi.radicalwing/photos/a.309038275950197/1091185011068849/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：陳奕齊 - 新一<br />\n<br />\n「越來越多香港人逃亡到台灣....」<br />\n香港，究竟怎麼了？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t50/1/16/1f525.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft50%2F1%2F16%2F1f525.png&h=20a13a3c&s={SIZE}\" /> 直播將視訊訪問 #林榮基 先生<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t50/1/16/1f525.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft50%2F1%2F16%2F1f525.png&h=20a13a3c&s={SIZE}\" /> #李倩怡 將現聲說法<br />\n<br />\n還記得四年前在香港「#被失蹤」的銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基嗎？他近日選擇 #流亡台灣；<br />\n<br />\n二年前，一位十八歲的香港少女李倩怡，因參與魚蛋革命被司法追殺，選擇流亡，至今仍下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n當時，林榮基先生依然樂觀地勸李倩怡回香港接受審判。而現在，《#逃犯條例》即將通過，促成10多萬香港人上街的「反送中」遊行。許多香港的朋友焦急地警告台灣，因為我們未來在香港，將可能直接被中共因政治因素隨意逮人。<br />\n<br />\n這兩位香港流亡者，希望對台灣訴說的心聲是什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n這個週二晚上八點半，我們直播見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sETkjGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsETkjGG.jpg&h=70f44172&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d1762ea74d3f7425472f1d00996441960438c01","tid":1140782,"uid":47714,"like